name: Nora Hepsie [Nobody]
description:
My "first succesful" attempt that produce good faces.

It doesn't match the exactly the real person face I trained it on, but it produce some good faces quite consistent, when you use the same model.

Trained with a big dataset of 105 images at 13125 steps of the same real person.

We'll see if someone finds who => please guesses in private comments ;) feel free to play guessing game

Hope you enjoy it !

PS: I'm not fully happy of the result yet: the training was planned for way more steps, but I stopped the training by accident. I'm still trying some stuff to compliment the training.
So maybe a new version might come along.
